        </div>

        <div class="footer-bottom">
          <p class="footer-copy">
            &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Tecil Integrated Services Limited. All rights reserved. &nbsp;·&nbsp;
            <a href="https://www.tecilsolar.com">www.tecilsolar.com</a>
